{"tid":2291104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"理⼤圍城⼀周年","createTime":"2020-11-18T13:35:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T12:30:01.000Z","uid":308710,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"46373d50314564195f954a18b3259ae3b2dc06e1","tid":2291104,"uid":308710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T13:35:48.000Z","msg":"一年後，你是忘記了，還是害怕想起來？<br />\n只希望當日喺埋土同埋出嚟迎救嘅手足都健健康康，平平安安。<br />\n<br />\n睇fb咁啱睇到篇文章，內文好值得大家一睇。<br />\n希望大家都肯click入去睇睇。<br />\n<br />\n要記住，大部分人都不願付出，結果只會所有人都一無所獲。<br />\n<br />\n「願你們都能感受那份慚愧，請不要放棄手足，也不要比手足更早放棄。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://fb.watch/1QSZtSopBR/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffb.watch%2F1QSZtSopBR%2F&d=VbAd486K8RrC2DEUtq3b5vsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=ccd21249\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fb.watch/1QSZtSopBR/</a>"},{"pid":"a052e8b02537ea1b3840801ec0e95e0b1903ca9b","tid":2291104,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T13:36:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"544602c63fbee83e925c668753c65913e095f834","tid":2291104,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T13:37:10.000Z","msg":"希望大家平平安安<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"693595c5c80b43ee5186f335a5ce39ad76c62ad6","tid":2291104,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T13:41:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d7237b7ba3bd63e5187d8614b860a35799f63d6","tid":2291104,"uid":280525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T13:51:42.000Z","msg":"好多都未必想回想 但會記住 <br />\n然後帶住向前行<br />\n最緊要抓緊你嘅信念 <img src